summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of the alley in Block Thirty-seven (37) Capitol Hill Addition, Division No. 5, in the City of Seattle, by paving and under Ordinance No. 26226, creating Local Improvement District No. 2444 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
